    public abstract class AbstractIndexedTransitionProvider<T extends Indexed,K>
extends java.lang.Object
implements TransitionProvider<K,T>, Contexed
    Abstract base class for building TransitionProviders on Indexed objects. unlike SimpleTransitionProvider this makes no assumption about the type used as the key
